reviews.text: Decent service, but misleading menu. I ordered some steak that was meant to come with fried bacon, mushroom and onions. The menu, both English and Chinese, and the pictures showed the fried stuff... But when the food came, they were all missing. When I asked the manager about this, he said 'yea, we don't do these fried stuff during lunch'. Misleading, be careful.

Absolute travesty of Italian classics. Since when was carbonara = scrambled eggs + noodles. Also, it wasn’t that good. Shame on the quality control. Avoid this place. It’s expensive and can’t seem to get their food right.
Very friendly staff,  always a pleasure to go there! The food is ok,  convenient to go there
Confortable seats, nice food. Afternoon tea is cheap and the noodles smells really good and tastes good. You can get a bowl of noodles with tea/coffee for just around 40HKD in afternoon tea time.

reviews.text: It's been a long time I had dinner here. The food still very delicious. No need to wait long queue.
taste good
我今日係呢度食嘢，大概1點10，行去出收銀，我小朋友跌咗張500蚊，三圍著黑色衫嘅男同事，佢話見唔到我小朋友揸住錢出嚟， 跟住我行出門口，有啲客喺度等緊位，跟住我細細聲問佢哋，是但一位女士，個女士話，你個小朋友行出嚟係冇錢，跟住我決定咗報警，跟住有個顧客，就肯攞返出嚟，我唔知佢係咪識佢。
員工態度一般，88蚊双扒午餐份量同下午茶餐一樣，亦冇解釋原來可以加飯或意粉，只有幫手了解問題的職員一人用心，如果同一般茶記一樣，可必要比88蚊受氣，可以同紅螞蟻拜拜喇

幾好味!
但環境欠佳!我坐下吃的時候見到有幾隻蒼蠅在我身邊飛來飛😱

reviews.text: 未去過但是都喜歡食，有機會去試下

Decent service, but misleading menu. I ordered some steak that was meant to come with fried bacon, mushroom and onions. The menu, both English and Chinese, and the pictures showed the fried stuff... But when the food came, they were all missing. When I asked the manager about this, he said 'yea, we don't do these fried stuff during lunch'. Misleading, be careful.

很差勁，點了個豬手套餐。 十幾分鐘後餐飲和餐湯都到了，之後才跟我說豬手賣完。羅宋湯超咸，不知所謂。 後來改點了落曼第豬扒餐，$128元 。是以下圖這一碟東西，我家樓下茶餐廳的豬扒飯 都比他大塊  
不會再來。 水平以下。超垃圾
這間餐廳內的餐牌令人費解 只可選擇下款其中一樣，想加錢要個湯佢又話我不是叫主餐牌無 法加，下次再來的機會比較微so sad😡😡😡
